displayProperties.name: Chaotic Exchanger
displayProperties.description: Resist incoming damage while charging your Void grenade. Charged Void grenades return grenade energy on a hit.

displayProperties.name: Upgrade Ghost
displayProperties.description: Upgrade this Ghost to increase its energy capacity by 1. Fully upgrading this Ghost to Masterwork provides an additional mod socket.

displayProperties.name: The Dance
displayProperties.description: Activating your dodge ability while near targets allows you to dodge additional times for a short period. Defeating targets extends the duration of the additional dodge.

displayProperties.name: Glacial Guard
displayProperties.description: Replaces your Barricade ability with a personal overshield. When you activate your Barricade, you create a burst around yourself that slows combatants. While you have the overshield, you are slowed and Barricade does not recharge.

displayProperties.name: Halberdier's Reach
displayProperties.description: Increases Glaive reload speed and melee damage when surrounded. Glaive melee final blows overflow a round to the magazine. Glaive projectile final blows detonate if the Glaive deals damage matching your subclass type.

displayProperties.name: Peregrine Strike
displayProperties.description: All shoulder charge abilities (Seismic Strike, Hammer Strike, or Shield Bash) deal bonus damage when activated in the air. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Activity Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Activity mods provide additional currency and material rewards in various activities.

displayProperties.name: Vanishing Execution
displayProperties.description: Powered melee final blows grant invisibility and restore a portion of health and shields. Finishers and final blows against more powerful targets increase the duration of the invisibility and the amount of health and shields restored.

displayProperties.name: Reflective Vents
displayProperties.description: Improved slide. Sliding after sprinting for a short time reflects incoming projectiles.

displayProperties.name: Bring the Heat
displayProperties.description: Fusion Grenades now explode on impact and gain increased throw speed. Final blows with Fusion Grenades grant grenade energy.

displayProperties.name: Burning Fists
displayProperties.description: Melee kills increase melee damage for a period of time. Additional kills extend duration and increase effects.

displayProperties.name: Scatter Charge
displayProperties.description: You gain an additional Scatter Grenade charge. Enables tracking for Scatter Grenade projectiles.

displayProperties.name: Wish-Dragon Teeth
displayProperties.description: Increases Tripmine Grenade duration and blast radius. Ability damage grants Tripmine Grenade energy.

displayProperties.name: Spring-Loaded Mounting
displayProperties.description: Increases Sidearm ready and reload speed. While you're critically wounded, swapping to a Sidearm increases its damage. Provides a large benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Sidearms.

displayProperties.name: Beyond The Veil
displayProperties.description: You gain a second Smoke Bomb charge and have damage resistance while invisible. When you make an ally invisible, they gain damage resistance while invisible and you gain melee energy.

displayProperties.name: Force Multiplier
displayProperties.description: While using a Void subclass, rapid Shotgun final blows or defeating a powerful combatant with a Shotgun will grant a Void overshield and start health regeneration. While you have a Void overshield, Shotguns deal additional damage, and Shotgun final blows refresh the overshield. Provides a moderate benefit to Shotgun airborne effectiveness and reload speed.

displayProperties.name: Wraithmetal Mail
displayProperties.description: Dodging reloads all weapons and increases both movement and weapon handling speeds for a brief time.

displayProperties.name: Synapse Junctions
displayProperties.description: Quick successive attacks with Arc Staff increase its damage output and duration.

displayProperties.name: Probability Matrix
displayProperties.description: Increases the chaining capabilities of Arc Bolt Grenade and has a chance to recharge it each time it deals damage. A full chain always recharges.

displayProperties.name: Cross Counter
displayProperties.description: Using your Arc melee ability or being hit by a melee attack will allow you to follow up with an extremely powerful melee counterpunch that will heal you.

displayProperties.name: Warlord's End
displayProperties.description: Powered melee final blows create a burst of energy that weakens nearby targets. Finishers and final blows against more powerful targets increase the radius of the burst and the length of the weakening effect.

displayProperties.name: Light Shift
displayProperties.description: Replaces your Stasis subclass Dodge ability with a longer range, faster moving shift that partially cloaks you during use. After shifting, your Stasis and Arc weapons deal increased damage for a short time.

displayProperties.name: Vengeance
displayProperties.description: Highlights the target who dares to damage you. Track down and destroy them for an overshield.

displayProperties.name: Default Ornament
displayProperties.description: Restores your armor to its default appearance.

displayProperties.name: Dearly Departed
displayProperties.description: Your Rift provides damage reduction to allied Guardians standing in it. Grants Rift energy when you are critically wounded. On your death, creates a healing rift on your corpse.

displayProperties.name: Tracking Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Tracking mods increase the range of the detection of caches and resources out in the field.

displayProperties.name: Seriously, Watch Out
displayProperties.description: Grants an overshield when you're sprinting at full health with Seismic Strike, Hammer Strike, or Shield Bash equipped and charged. Hits with these abilities recharge a portion of your melee energy.

displayProperties.name: Tight Fit
displayProperties.description: Dodging boosts reload speed, handling, and airborne effectiveness for you and nearby allies. While the buff is active, final blows and additional dodges increase the buff strength and refresh the timer. Maxes out at 5 stacks.

displayProperties.name: And Another Thing
displayProperties.description: Gain an additional grenade charge.

displayProperties.name: Rapid Cooldown
displayProperties.description: Increased grenade, melee, and dodge regeneration while sprinting. Dodging increases your sprint speed.

displayProperties.name: Blessing of Order
displayProperties.description: Standing in a healing rift creates Noble Seekers that seek out allies that are not in a rift and heal them. Standing in an empowering rift creates Noble Seekers that grant both you and your ally a damage bonus. Each time a Noble Seeker finds one of your allies, the duration of your rift is briefly extended while you are standing in it. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of the Hand Cannon Lumina.

displayProperties.name: Kill Tracker
displayProperties.description: This weapon tracks the number of enemies you defeated with it.

displayProperties.name: Puppeteer's Control
displayProperties.description: Drengr's Lash spawns two additional projectiles, tracks targets more aggressively, and travels farther. Gain Woven Mail when suspending targets.

displayProperties.name: Fervid Coldsnap
displayProperties.description: Your Coldsnap grenades have an additional charge that recharges quicker on direct impact. The seeker spawned from Coldsnap grenades travels further.

displayProperties.name: Tome of Dawn
displayProperties.description: When Dawnblade is equipped, aiming weapons while you're midair suspends you there for a short time, improving airborne accuracy, reducing incoming flinch, and granting damage resistance. Weapon hits extend this effect's duration. Provides a large benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Fusion Harness
displayProperties.description: Fusion Grenades have an additional charge and recharge from empowered weapon damage, with empowered weapon final blows granting more energy. Fusion Grenade final blows grant Rift energy.

displayProperties.name: Resolute
displayProperties.description: Arc final blows grant an escalating damage bonus with Arc weapons. Gain an overshield when activating Fists of Havoc, and gain the highest tier damage bonus to Arc weapons when your Fists of Havoc Super ends.

displayProperties.name: Hand-Laid Stock
displayProperties.description:
This weapon is optimized for recoil control.
  •  Increases stability

displayProperties.name: Empty Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: No mod currently selected.

displayProperties.name: Appended Mag
displayProperties.description:
This weapon's magazine is built for higher capacity.
  •  Increases magazine size

displayProperties.name: Embers of Light
displayProperties.description: While Daybreak is active, defeating combatants or Guardians creates a Healing and Empowering Rift at their location. Solar weapon final blows grant Rift energy, granting more when you are standing in any Rift. When your Rift energy is full and you are standing in any Rift, final blows consume your class energy and create a healing and empowering rift at the target's location.

displayProperties.name: Planetary Torrent
displayProperties.description: Rifts periodically release Arc shockwaves. Final blows with these shockwaves create an Arc explosion. While an Arc subclass is equipped, the shockwaves and subsequent explosions blind nearby targets. Rift energy recharges faster when you are surrounded by targets.

displayProperties.name: Cobra Totemic
displayProperties.description: Weapons ready and reload very quickly. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Biotic Enhancements
displayProperties.description: Increased melee lunge range. Improved melee and Super damage when you're surrounded.

displayProperties.name: Fury Conductors
displayProperties.description: Melee hits build energy. Being struck by a melee attack reduces incoming damage and unleashes the energy in a devastating explosion.

displayProperties.name: Horns of Doom
displayProperties.description:
Void melee kills give Super energy.
While Sentinel Shield is active, melee kills recharge Shield Throw, which extends your Super on hits.

displayProperties.name: Cauterizing Flame
displayProperties.description: When you are critically wounded with full class ability energy or when you cast a Barricade, create a Sunspot at your location that has improved restoration effects.

displayProperties.name: Ascending Amplitude
displayProperties.description: Each target you defeat with Stormtrance increases the damage you deal with it and refunds Super energy when Stormtrance ends.

displayProperties.name: Starless Night
displayProperties.description: Targets that enter Ward of Dawn are blinded, while allies that pass through gain a Void overshield. Guarding with Sentinel Shield blinds nearby targets.

displayProperties.name: Devouring Rift
displayProperties.description: Casting an empowering rift will grant you Devour. Damage dealt by you and your allies from within your empowering rift will disrupt combatants.

displayProperties.name: Ionic Conductor
displayProperties.description: Ionic traces you create move faster and grant you additional ability energy. Nearby allies also gain ability energy when you collect an ionic trace.

displayProperties.name: Overcharge Capacitor
displayProperties.description: Sprinting, sliding, and firing this weapon builds a temporary electrostatic charge, increasing range and reload speed. Final blows with high charge cause explosions, and maximum charge explosions blind targets.

displayProperties.name: Default Effect
displayProperties.description: Use default transmat effects when arriving in a location or reviving.

displayProperties.name: Blood Magic
displayProperties.description: While standing in any rift, gain a bonus to weapons with a damage type matching your subclass damage type. Weapon final blows while standing in any rift pause the rift's countdown, extending its duration.

displayProperties.name: Myrmidon's Reach
displayProperties.description:
Gain a second charge of your Shield Throw melee. Your Shield Throw melee now weakens targets and becomes shield-piercing, stunning [Shield-Piercing] Barrier Champions. 

When you stun a [Shield-Piercing] Barrier Champion with your Shield Throw melee, you regain a melee charge.

displayProperties.name: Adamantine Brace
displayProperties.description: Bow charges can be held indefinitely. Gain a bonus to the Bow's damage when released, based on how long the charge was held. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Bows.

displayProperties.name: Sharp Edges
displayProperties.description: Hits and kills with Blade Barrage will return Super energy after the Super ends.

displayProperties.name: Depths of Duskfield
displayProperties.description: Your Duskfield grenades have a much larger effect radius. Allies inside the Duskfield take reduced damage and targets inside the area deal reduced damage.

displayProperties.name: Empty Catalyst Socket
displayProperties.description:
An Exotic catalyst can be inserted into this socket.

Check the Exotic catalysts section in Triumphs to learn where the catalyst can be obtained.

displayProperties.name: Lancer's Vigil
displayProperties.description: Diamond Lances create Stasis crystals on impact when thrown, with more crystals created by hitting bosses and vehicles. While using a Stasis subclass and behind your rally barricade, rapid precision hits and combatant final blows with a Stasis weapon creates a Diamond Lance near you.

displayProperties.name: Sunfire Furnace
displayProperties.description: Improves the recharge rate of your Solar abilities. Greatly improves recharge rate while your Super is charged. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Survival Well
displayProperties.description: Generates an additional Orb of Power from Supers and a healing pulse when Barricade is activated.

displayProperties.name: Auto-Loading Link
displayProperties.description: Steadily reloads a portion of your equipped Auto Rifle's or Machine Gun's magazine from reserves. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Auto Rifles and Machine Guns.

displayProperties.name: Economic Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Economic mods increase currency and resource gains from sources.

displayProperties.name: Illegally Modded Holster
displayProperties.description: When you ready a fully loaded Hand Cannon that deals Kinetic damage or a damage type that matches your subclass energy type, each hit from that Hand Cannon increases the damage of the next shot for a short time against a combatant. Hand Cannons ready faster and are more accurate immediately after swapping to them. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Hand Cannons while the buff is active.

displayProperties.name: Uncanny Arrows
displayProperties.description: Provides ability energy for each target tethered by Deadfall anchors. Moebius Quiver has an additional shot.

displayProperties.name: Hydraulic Boosters
displayProperties.description: While your Dodge energy is full, increases sprint speed and slide distance and improves High Jump, Strafe Jump, and Triple Jump.

displayProperties.name: Clenched Fist
displayProperties.description: Maximizes guard stats on equipped Swords. You take reduced damage while blocking with a Sword. Rapidly damaging targets after blocking shots with a Sword grants restoration for a duration determined by the number of shots blocked.

displayProperties.name: Empty Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: No mod currently selected.

displayProperties.name: Assault Barricade
displayProperties.description: You and allies can shoot through your Towering Barricade, which has an increased cooldown and reduced health and duration.

displayProperties.name: Parting Gift
displayProperties.description:
Dodging leaves behind an explosive that detonates after a short delay, damaging targets around it and creating a secondary effect based on your subclass energy type:
• [Arc] Blinds targets.
• [Solar] Scorches targets.
• [Void] Suppresses targets.
• [Stasis] Slows targets.
• [Strand] Severs targets.

displayProperties.name: Overflowing Light
displayProperties.description: Using an ability (grenade, melee, or Barricade) empowers the other two abilities. Empowered means abilities have faster regen, melees and grenades do more damage, and Barricades have more hit points.

displayProperties.name: Close Enough
displayProperties.description: Damaging targets with Chaos Reach extends its duration.

displayProperties.name: Hammer of the Gods
displayProperties.description: Defeating targets with your Thunderclap melee restores melee energy. Targets near you when you use your Thunderclap suffer lightning strikes and become jolted; being amplified increases the damage of these lightning strikes.

displayProperties.name: The Fourth Magic
displayProperties.description: Weapon final blows with a damage type matching your subclass energy grant Death Throes, which provides a grenade damage bonus and grants you grenade energy. When you have Death Throes and throw a grenade, nearby allies gain greatly increased grenade regeneration for a short time.

displayProperties.name: Empty Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: No mod currently selected.

displayProperties.name: Vanishing Shadow
displayProperties.description: Increases the duration of any invisibility effects. While you are invisible, your melee recharges faster, your weapons reload faster, and your Recovery is greatly increased.

displayProperties.name: Roast 'Em
displayProperties.description:
Your Proximity Knife scorches targets it damages with its explosions, or ignites targets on final blow.

After throwing a Proximity Knife, you gain increased melee regeneration until the knife explodes.

displayProperties.name: Roving Assassin
displayProperties.description: Each Spectral Blades kill you make before going into stealth will restore more of your Super energy.

displayProperties.name: Double Dodge
displayProperties.description: Gain a second dodge charge.

displayProperties.name: Crystalline Transistor
displayProperties.description: Precision final blows from Kinetic weapons create an explosion that deals damage in the element of your subclass and applies elemental effects.

displayProperties.name: Battle-Hearth
displayProperties.description: Kills and assists you make while standing in your Well of Radiance return Super energy.

displayProperties.name: High Priority
displayProperties.description: Steadily reloads a portion of your equipped Trace Rifles's magazine from reserves. Damaging a vehicle, boss, or champion with a trace rifle marks them as the target. When an ally defeats the marked target, generate special ammo for yourself and heavy ammo for your allies.

displayProperties.name: Destabilizers
displayProperties.description: [Brake]  : Use while airborne to release roll stabilizers, and move [Movement] to roll.

displayProperties.name: Random Mod
displayProperties.description: A mod with arbitrarily generated upgrades.

displayProperties.name: Solar Rampart
displayProperties.description: Solar final blows recharge your Barricade, which unleashes a blast of Solar energy that scorches targets when summoned.

displayProperties.name: No Projection
displayProperties.description: Restores your Ghost to an empty projection.

displayProperties.name: Barri-nade
displayProperties.description: Using your class ability channels defensive Light inward, providing a grenade that creates a barricade on impact.

displayProperties.name: Glacial Fortification
displayProperties.description: When using the Stasis subclass, your Barricade becomes a wall of Stasis crystals that slows nearby targets when created. Standing behind this barricade will grant you and your allies increased weapon reload speed, stability, and range.

displayProperties.name: Firewalker
displayProperties.description: Solar final blows periodically grant you an escalating bonus to weapon damage. You are harder to slow or freeze with Stasis, and when you break out, you take no damage from doing so, creating a burst of Solar energy around yourself.

displayProperties.name: Absorption Cells
displayProperties.description: Takedowns with weapons that have a damage type matching your subclass element grant you Super energy. While your Super energy is full, you instead gain a temporary bonus to weapon damage of the type matching your subclass element.

displayProperties.name: The Whispers
displayProperties.description: Gain an additional melee charge. Charged melee final blows spawn an Orb of Power.

displayProperties.name: Relentless Tracker
displayProperties.description: Visually marks targets. Deals more damage to low-health marked targets. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Hawkeye Hack
displayProperties.description: Modifies Golden Gun to fire a single high-damage shot. Enemies eliminated by the shot explode and grant you Super energy.

displayProperties.name: Upgraded Sensor Pack
displayProperties.description: Provides radar while you're aiming. Enhances your radar resolution while crouched.

displayProperties.name: Warlord's Sigil
displayProperties.description: Eliminating enemies with melee attacks increases your melee damage.

displayProperties.name: Vampire's Caress
displayProperties.description: Melee kills instantly restore a large amount of health and continue to restore health afterwards for a short duration.

displayProperties.name: Helium Spirals
displayProperties.description: Increases the duration of Solar Grenades. Solar melee kills grant unlimited Solar Grenade energy for a brief time.

displayProperties.name: Rites of Ember
displayProperties.description: Your Daybreak projectiles deal more damage and scorch targets on impact. Your scorch is improved and you gain a small amount of melee energy when your scorch damages a target.

displayProperties.name: Swarmers
displayProperties.description: Destroying a Tangle spawns a Threadling. Your Threadlings unravel targets that they damage.

displayProperties.name: Regenerative Motion
displayProperties.description: Sprinting gradually reloads this weapon.

displayProperties.name: Nightmare Fuel
displayProperties.description: Dealing melee damage reloads your currently equipped weapon. Charged melee final blows reload all weapons. Provides a large benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons, and movement speed and jump height after dealing melee damage.

displayProperties.name: Dynamic Duo
displayProperties.description: [Grenade]  : Convert your Arc grenade into a Arc Soul and become amplified. The Arc Soul functions as an autonomous turret.

displayProperties.name: Hearts of Ice
displayProperties.description: Your Winter's Wrath Shockwave deals increased shatter damage. Allies in range of your Shockwave gain an overshield and increased damage with Stasis weapons.

displayProperties.name: Default Ornament
displayProperties.description: Restores your weapon to its default appearance.

displayProperties.name: Beacons of Empowerment
displayProperties.description: Sol Invictus lasts twice as long. Allies who pass through your Sunspot are granted Sol Invictus and Solar restoration.

displayProperties.name: Custom Drive
displayProperties.description: An expertly tuned NLS drive, providing the best possible performance.

displayProperties.name: Kintsugi
displayProperties.description: Final blows from weapons with a damage type matching your subclass energy create a burst of healing around you. After reviving or being revived, you gain an aura that provides overshields to you and nearby allies.

displayProperties.name: Jump Jets
displayProperties.description: Provides additional aerial maneuverability and enables accurate hipfire while you're in the air during Lift. Provides a large benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons while hipfiring.

displayProperties.name: Mecha Holster
displayProperties.description: Reloads stowed Submachine Guns and allows you to ready them instantly. Improves your handling with Submachine Guns and your movement while wielding one. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Submachine Guns.

displayProperties.name: Linear Actuators
displayProperties.description: Increases sprint speed. Sprinting builds up a static charge. After melee-attacking an enemy, that charge will chain damage to nearby enemies.

displayProperties.name: Sect of Force
displayProperties.description: You specialize in punishing powerful combatants before they can harm your allies.

displayProperties.name: Move to Survive
displayProperties.description: Blink further and more frequently. Weapon readies quickly out of Blink and radar remains up. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Alchemical Etchings
displayProperties.description: Your Rifts gain the additional ability to increase weapon reload speeds. Empowering Rift makes weapons effective over longer ranges.

displayProperties.name: Strange Protractor
displayProperties.description: Sprint speed increased. After a short time sprinting, your currently equipped weapon is automatically reloaded.

displayProperties.name: Spheromatik Trigger
displayProperties.description: Powered melee final blows unleash a damaging explosion. Finishers and final blows against more powerful targets increase the radius and damage of the explosion.

displayProperties.name: Upgrade Armor
displayProperties.description: Upgrade this armor to increase its energy capacity by 1. Fully upgrading this armor will forge a Masterwork, which provides a bonus to all stats.

displayProperties.name: Activity Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Available once the Ghost shell has been fully Masterworked.

displayProperties.name: Voltaic Mirror
displayProperties.description: Attacks you redirect with your Arc Staff deal massively increased damage and generate Orbs of Power for your allies. Guarding with your Arc Staff does not consume extra Super energy.

displayProperties.name: Dreaded Visage
displayProperties.description: Grants ability energy when you're damaged. When critically wounded, regain maximum health on kills.

displayProperties.name: Transfusion Matrix
displayProperties.description: Kills with Arc melee abilities trigger health regeneration and restore melee energy.

displayProperties.name: Skittering Stinger
displayProperties.description:
Weighted Knife gains a second bounce. Rapid precision hits with your weapons grant Weighted Knife a significant damage bonus, bonus strength, and the ability to stun unshielded combatants for a short time.

Empowered Weighted Knife is strong against [Stagger] Unstoppable Champions.

displayProperties.name: Scissor Fingers
displayProperties.description: Grants two knives per charge.

displayProperties.name: Burning Souls
displayProperties.description: Dodging gives a small health and shield bump.

displayProperties.name: See Me, Feel Me
displayProperties.description: Your Void weapons gain Volatile Rounds after you emerge from being invisible. When you are invisible and defeat a combatant while using a finisher, all of your weapons gain bonus damage; you and your nearby allies gain a reserve overshield and improved class ability regeneration. These reserve overshields can be deployed by using a class ability.

displayProperties.name: Empty Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: No mod currently selected.

displayProperties.name: Grasp of the Devourer
displayProperties.description:
Damaging combatants poisons them, dealing increasing damage over time. Defeating a poisoned combatant spreads the condition.

Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all Weapons of Sorrow.

displayProperties.name: New Tricks
displayProperties.description: Improves Skip Grenade, and you gain an additional Skip Grenade charge. Skip Grenade returns energy when it damages enemies.

displayProperties.name: Cerebral Uplink
displayProperties.description: Highlights priority targets and improves the regeneration speed of your grenade, melee, and Rift abilities. Provides a small benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of all weapons.

displayProperties.name: Abyssal Extractors
displayProperties.description: Void-damage kills increase ability energy recharge rate.

displayProperties.name: Actual Grandeur
displayProperties.description: Provides additional damage resistance during Nova Bomb. Nova Bomb kills grant Super energy.

displayProperties.name: Conduction Tines
displayProperties.description: Arc ability or jolt final blows increase the recharge rate of your Arc abilities and extend the duration of Stormtrance.

displayProperties.name: Misdirection
displayProperties.description: Dodging disorients nearby enemies and temporarily removes their radar.

displayProperties.name: Feast of Light
displayProperties.description: You gain additional Super energy from Orbs of Power you pick up. While your Super energy is full, picking up an Orb of Power overcharges your Super, causing you to gain a burst of healing when cast and a bonus to your Super damage. At maximum overcharge, you also gain an overshield.

displayProperties.name: Corkscrew Rifling
displayProperties.description:
Balanced barrel. 
  •  Slightly increases range and stability
  •  Slightly increases handling speed

displayProperties.name: Touch of Venom
displayProperties.description: Punching someone with full melee energy will instantly cast Smoke Bomb. Your Smoke Bombs deal increased damage, regenerate more quickly when stuck to a surface, and grant you Truesight after damaging a target.

displayProperties.name: Acrobat's Focus
displayProperties.description: Gain Woven Mail when activating grapple. Increased flinch resistance while Woven Mail is active.

displayProperties.name: Insatiable
displayProperties.description: Immediately regenerate health, melee, grenade, and Rift energy upon activating your Super. Nearby allies recharge class abilities faster.

displayProperties.name: Ursine Guard
displayProperties.description: Move faster while guarding when Sentinel Shield is active. Guarded damage converts to Super energy when the Super ends.

displayProperties.name: Experience Mod Socket
displayProperties.description: Experience mods increase global experience gains.

displayProperties.name: Soaring Fusilier
displayProperties.description: Air dodge reloads all of your weapons and improves the airborne effectiveness of Fusion Rifles and Linear Fusion Rifles; final blows with these weapons make you radiant. Provides a moderate benefit to the airborne effectiveness stat of Fusion Rifles and Linear Fusion Rifles.

displayProperties.name: Glorious Charge
displayProperties.description: Greatly increases your Thundercrash impact damage. Gain an overshield that lasts longer the farther you travel before striking a target.

displayProperties.name: Default Shader
displayProperties.description: Restores your gear to its default colors.

displayProperties.name: Mobius Conduit
displayProperties.description: [Super]  : Deactivate Arc Staff early to create a blinding explosion and gain a temporary boost to Arc weapon damage. Arc Staff consumes energy more slowly when not attacking.
